# --- Tracked pipeline outputs (small, write-once; weights/models stay ignored above) ---
# Concept vectors + activations + meta per model
# Re-include the directory first, then its contents (gitignore last-match-wins).
!data/processed/concept_vectors/
!data/processed/concept_vectors/**
!data/processed/concept_vectors_*/
!data/processed/concept_vectors_*/**
# Deterministic validation logs, metric tables (CSV), and layer-sweep outputs
!results/logs/validate_probes_*.json
!results/tables/probe_metrics*.csv
!results/tables/layer_sweep*.csv
!results/tables/layer_sweep*.meta.json
